Package: dynamicmultiplex
Title: Community detection for identifying communities in evolving networked systems
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Jared",
           family = "Edgerton",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "jared.edgerton@gmail.com")
Description: Multiplex temporal community detection with customizable interlayer coupling. Runs Louvain or Leiden community detection on each network layer and constructs interlayer ties using Jaccard similarity, overlap coefficient, node-strength weighted variants, or direct node identity links. Supports user-specified layer connectivity via the layer_links argument, enabling adjacent-only temporal coupling that avoids the long-range pooling problem in standard multislice approaches.
